# Sitecore Rules

See the repo-root `.cursor/rules/sitecore.mdc` for shared Sitecore XM Cloud patterns.

Key rules for this starter:
- SDK: `@sitecore-content-sdk/nextjs`
- Props: extend `ComponentProps` from `@/lib/component-props`
- Fields: always use SDK editable helpers (`Text`, `RichText`, `NextImage`, `Link`)
- Variants: named exports (`export const Default`), never `export default`
- Datasource: check `fields?.data?.datasource` before rendering, use `NoDataFallback`
- Edit mode: `useSitecore()` hook, check `page.mode.isEditing`
- Styling: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui from `@/components/ui/*`
